## Give by Mail

Send your tax-deductible gift to:

**Camp Otyokwah**
**3380 Tugend Rd**
**Butler, OH 44822**

Make checks payable to "Camp Otyokwah."

Questions? Contact us at info@otyokwah.org or (419) 883-3854.
{% /gridSquare %}
