## Pop Tewell Campership Fund

Help send a child to camp who otherwise couldn't afford it. Named in honor of Pop Tewell, this fund provides scholarships for campers in need — giving every child the chance to experience the life-changing power of Christian camping.

{% ctaButton
   label="Support the Campership Fund"
   href="https://www.ultracamp.com/clientlogin.aspx?idCamp=1342&campCode=OTY"
   variant="inverse"
   size="lg"
   textColor="secondary" /%}
{% /gridSquare %}

